<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>发动机虚拟装配系统 - 3D模型</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;700&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/scifi-theme.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/model.css">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- 科幻风格导航栏 -->
  <nav class="scifi-nav">
    <div class="nav-container">
      <div class="nav-logo">
        <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
        <span>发动机虚拟装配系统</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="nav-link"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> 主页</a>
        <a href="/gallery" class="nav-link"><i class="fas fa-images"></i> 图库</a>
        <a href="/game" class="nav-link"><i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i> 工位空间布局</a>
        <a href="/model" class="nav-link active"><i class="fas fa-cube"></i> 3D模型</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="user-panel">
        <span class="username"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> <%= username %></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>
  
  <!-- 主要内容 -->
  <div class="model-page-content">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>发动机3D模型交互</h1>
      <p>通过3D模型详细了解发动机结构，实时操作和探索各个组件</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 模型展示区 -->
    <div class="model-display">
      <div class="model-container">
        <div class="model-aspect-ratio">
          <iframe class="model-iframe" src="/unity/index.html" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="model-controls">
        <div class="control-group">
          <div class="control-title">操作指南</div>
          <div class="control-items">
            <div class="control-item">
              <div class="control-icon"><i class="fas fa-mouse"></i></div>
              <div class="control-text">左键拖动：旋转视角</div>
            </div>
            <div class="control-item">
              <div class="control-icon"><i class="fas fa-search-plus"></i></div>
              <div class="control-text">滚轮：缩放模型</div>
            </div>
            <div class="control-item">
              <div class="control-icon"><i class="fas fa-object-ungroup"></i></div>
              <div class="control-text">右键：展开/收起爆炸图</div>
            </div>
            <div class="control-item">
              <div class="control-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-pointer"></i></div>
              <div class="control-text">点击部件：查看详情</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 模型信息 -->
    <div class="model-info-section">
      <div class="scifi-grid scifi-grid-2">
        <div class="scifi-card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="card-title">模型描述</h3>
          </div>
          <p>这是一个高精度的发动机3D模型，包含了发动机的所有主要组件和零部件。通过这个模型，您可以详细了解发动机的内部结构、各部件的空间关系以及装配顺序。模型支持实时交互，可以缩放、旋转和分解，以便从各个角度观察发动机的细节。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="scifi-card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="card-title">技术规格</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="tech-specifications">
            <div class="spec-item">
              <div class="spec-label">模型精度</div>
              <div class="spec-value">±0.01mm</div>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <div class="spec-label">零部件数量</div>
              <div class="spec-value">217</div>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <div class="spec-label">多边形数量</div>
              <div class="spec-value">1,243,780</div>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <div class="spec-label">材质数量</div>
              <div class="spec-value">54</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- 科幻风格页脚 -->
  <footer class="scifi-footer">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-logo">BUAA工业设计系发动机虚拟装配课题组</div>
      <div class="footer-info">先进技术 · 精密工程 · 虚拟现实</div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="footer-link">主页</a>
        <a href="/gallery" class="footer-link">图库</a>
        <a href="/game" class="footer-link">工位空间布局</a>
        <a href="/model" class="footer-link">3D模型</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copyright">© BUAA工业设计系发动机虚拟装配课题组. 保留所有权利.</div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>